C  Gilbert Eigenhuis  Jr





 






5 Stars Out Of 5






March 12, 2009



C  Gilbert Eigenhuis  Jr






  
            James Edwards' presentation of the Gospel of Mark is refreshing and equally stimulating.  His scholastic disciplines are evident, yet his material is readable and can be understood by those just beginning their walk of faith.  I recommend this work to any seeking a deeper understanding of the importance of this Gospel.
        














